    "Line Have Musaeus, Ole Sejer Iversen Over the last few years the availability and usability of generative AI systems have increased tremendously, impacting everybody's lives, also the everyday lives of students.",
    "Hence, there is a growing call for teaching about AI in computing education (Tedre et al., 2021).",
    "Research on how to teach about generative AI systems and not only about the use of generative AI is increasing in computing education research, and there are now an interesting array of approaches to teaching about AI.",
    "This body of research allows us, as researchers, to focus our concentration on questions such as: What kind of tools can support students in being designers and creators of AI systems?",
    "What and how can students learn about generative AI systems when interacting with such tools in various subjects?"
  ],
